Mac:
Common:
cmd-d delete selected lines
cmd-shift-d duplecate lines
cmd-right move to end of the line
cmd-left move to start of the line
选取1行  cmd L ，继续按，会继续选取下一行
删除当前字符到行首  cmd delete
删除当前字符到行尾  cmd fn delete
全局查找 cmd shift f

ctrl-uparrow 与上一行互换
ctrl-downarrow 与下一行互换
ctrl-enter 光标下面新建一行
ctrl-shift-enter 光标上面新建一行
ctrl-tab switch tabs
ctrl-| tooggle tree


Not very common:
搜索文件 cmd p
打开一个目录 cmd o
跳转到指定行 ctrl g
